text:
1. Pick up toothbrush.
2. Apply toothpaste to the toothbrush.
3. Wet the toothbrush with water.
4. Place the toothbrush in the mouth.
5. Move the toothbrush back and forth across the teeth.
6. Brush the front and back surfaces of the teeth.
7. Brush the chewing surfaces of the teeth.
8. Brush the tongue.
9. Spit out the toothpaste and rinse the mouth with water.
10. Rinse the toothbrush and put it back in its holder.
